<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٨٨]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«أنيب»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{أَوْ قَوْمَ صَالِحٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٨٩]</span> حسن.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
